Class Summary
DatabaseConnection The Class DatabaseConnection starts the http client to acess the couchdb database.
NumberType The Class NumberType defines the document formats for the number value documents stored in the couchdb database.
NumberType.Avg The Class Avg defines the avg format of the documents in couchdb.
NumberType.DateAvg The Class DateAvg defines the dateavg format of the documents in couchdb.
NumberType.DateMax The Class DateMax defines the datemax format of the documents in couchdb.
NumberType.DateMin The Class DateMin defines the datemin format of the documents in couchdb.
NumberType.DateSum The Class DateSum defines the datesum format of the documents in couchdb.
NumberType.Default The Class Default defines the default format for a number value document stored in the couchdb database.
NumberType.Max The Class Max defines the sum format of the documents in couchdb.
NumberType.Min The Class Min defines the sum format of the documents in couchdb.
NumberType.Sum The Class Sum defines the sum format of the documents in couchdb.
NumberTypeRepository The Class NumberTypeRepository contains the methods to connect to the couchdb database and store and retrieve data from it.
StringType The Class StringType defines the document formats for the string value documents stored in the couchdb database.
StringType.Default The Class Default defines the default format for a string value document stored in the couchdb database.
StringTypeRepository The Class StringTypeRepository contains the methods to connect to the couchdb database and store and retrieve data from it.
